snippet.title: Game Gear Longplay [049] Outrun
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mad-Matt

Extremely difficult version of the game for the trusty sega handheld. As if the game wouldn't be difficult enough with a small, blurry, laggy screen .... the time limit gives you no room error so dont at any point think about crashing if you want to reach the end goal.

4 routes shown and all 3 soundtracks.

00:00:00 Left -> Left -> Left -> Goal A (Magical Sound Shower)

00:11:05 Left -> Left -> Right -> Goal B (Passing Breeze)

00:21:05 Right -> Left -> Right -> Goal C (Splash Wave)

00:31:05 Right -> Right -> Right -> Goal D (Splash Wave) -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
